Okay, so before, I said that I looked like Lia from ITZY, but now people are telling me I look like Irene from Red Velvet, and Eun Bi from IZ*ONE. So uh, it basically means that I suck at seeing whether or not I look similar to an idol or not. Now that I look at my face, I do see Eun Bi and Irene more then Lia. So yea, I would say I look like Eun Bi/Irene. But we're gonna go deeper down. . . . Eyes: Irene  Okay, but our eyes look so goddam similar. Like idk what this is, but we both have these lump sorta things on the bottom lol. Not to mention I also have double eyelids, just like her. We have kinda big eyes. Edit: So I realised that those lump things are called aegyo-sal's (correct me if I'm wrong) Nose: Eun Bi  (Eun Bi is on the left)Our nose bridges are pretty similar. I feel like my nose looks like Irene's also, but more of Eun Bi's. Her side profile looks some what similar to mine. Our noses are pretty small also. Lips: Jisoo  We both have heart shaped lips. I think that hers is more heart shaped then mine, but mine is also heart shaped. Pretty thin lips, when I don't put heavy makeup on, which is similar to Jisoo. Face shape: Irene  Our face shapes are really similar. We both have an oval shape as our face shape, but it isn't too oval-y (lol my words). Our side profile is also pretty similar, and her bone structure is similar to mine. Overall: I feel like I look like Irene the most. Our face shape, and eyes are really similar. Our noses are pretty similar, and the only thing different are our lips. The reason why I said I look like Eun Bi too, is because I feel like Eun Bi looks like Irene, so I feel like I also look like her. . . . So to answer the question; Which K-Pop idol do people say look like you? My answer is Irene, and runner-up is Eun Bi. I actually thought I looked like Lia, but then when I went to Korea, people started complementing me for looking like Irene lol. Then when I actually looked closely, I realised that I did look like Irene (and Eun Bi) quite a lot. I think that I fit K-Standards pretty well actually, the only things I don't have, is that I have tanned skin. Thats basically it. I'm not tryna brag here or anything, I just wanted to point out something I found. But it does make sense since Irene fits K-Standards amazingly. Hope this answered your question! Stay safe everyone! <3

Background: I am Asian, but I won’t go into specifics since I want to keep a low profile. I am female btw. I won’t be showing photos of my face. I don’t exactly look like a Kpop idol, per se. But I do have individual features like some. Eyes: My eyes somewhat resemble Lisa of Blackpink.  Big but not too big - with a softer inner medial canthus (although the canthus on my right eye is kinda sharp) and thin double eyelids. The rest of my family have smaller eyes, so I don’t know where I got it from. Recessive genes? Nose: My nose looks like Got7’s Yugyeom,   I actually have a big nose for a female😭😭. I have a high bridged nose, rare in my family, and it does look a lot like Yugyeom’s. Lips: It is quite standard and nothing special lol. It does look a little like Lisa of Blackpink without lipstick etc.  It is similar in the sense that her lower lip is bigger than her upper lip like me; although I will say my lips are not as plump as hers. Skin tone: I would say I have it similar to Taehyung of BTS.   Without all the whitewash and filter, Taehyung’s natural skin pigmentation is similar to mine. Both of us share the same honey skin. I will say that I was actually pretty pale when I was little. Later, I moved to another country where the climate is unbelievably hot and dry. So I ended up becoming tanned, and I still am. I could name other idols like Twice’s Tzuyu, Jessi, Hwasa, etc., but I think my skin tone is more similar to him. Face shape/Jawline: Irene of Red Velvet.   I have a slim and small oval face shape with little to no chubby cheeks. I have a chiseled V shaped jawline which resembles Irene of Red Velvet. Of course, there are several other idols with the same face, but I relate to Irene’s the most. I will say that my jaw is a little more angular at the tip but that’s basically the only difference. Hair: I am going to insert a picture of my hair.  It’s shoulder length and mostly straight but not the silky and glossy kind if you know what I mean. I’m, pretty sure it looks exactly like Blackpink’s Jisoo in this picture.  I know she doesn’t have this hair currently, but I do have the same hair as hers in the picture, and her hair here fits the exact description of mine given above. It’s a tad bit silkier but not a big difference. Eyebrows: literally any female idol.  My eyes are pretty much straight and thinner naturally, and I can’t pinpoint one idol who has it since almost every female idol has them. Here is just an example for reference (Joy of Red Velvet.) Smile: Lisa of Blackpink.  I couldn’t think of a better one. She matches my smile the closest. Since we have almost the same lip shape, our smile is formed similarly (??) and it’s a bit gummy on the sides. thanks for reading! Also, I would like to see how close my real face would look like when compiled with all the specific features of the idols I mentioned above, but i don’t know how to do that, im pretty sure you should use some apps or sumn (?). if there is any photo editor here who is interested in doing this for free (im broke srry) please message me.
